originalText.text: My Daughter went to the Anderson School as a transfer Student for the 7th and 8th grade. It was an excellent experience for both the student and the parents. The best way that t can describe the experience: From the first email and first phone call (answered on one ring) to the graduation ceremony, everything was handled with efficiency, tact and intelligence. I perhaps called the school 3 or 4 times in the 2 years to get some information, every time I called the person who ANSWERED the phone had the answer! The education was excellent as well. The Anderson School may well be the best ORGANIZATION that I have EVER dealt with at any time.
